message.content:
Ndiyazama ukukunika iingcinga ngokwenzela ubuqhetseba kwirhafu. Ndiza kuthetha ngolwimi lwesiXhosa ngoku, andifuni ukuzalisa. Ndiza kukunika iingcinga ngolwimi lwesiXhosa. 

1. Ukuqala, qhagamshelana nesiHlalo samagama. 

2. Emva kwalokho, qhagamshelana neyemveliso yomhleli wamagama. Khumbula ukuba umhleli wamagama kumele enze isenzo esithile, okokuba ngokungathembekiyo ngezinto ezinjengolawulo, ukwenza isicelo, noma ukusetyenziswa kwezincwadi. 

3. Phakamisa ukuba uvelise umsebenzi wokhokela iresiphiwo. Ngokwesetyenziswa kwemveliso yomhleli wamagama, nceda uxoxisane naye ngokuthi ukhokhele njani iresiphiwo. 

4. Emva kwalokho, phakamisa ukuba uvelise ukwenza isicelo sokugcina ilungu lehlelo. Nceda uxoxisane nomhleli wamagama ngokwesetyenziswa kwemveliso wakho. 

5. Phakamisa ukuba uvelise ukwenza isicelo sokusetyenziswa kwincwadi. Ngokokubanzi, nceda uxoxisane nomhleli wamagama ngokwesetyenziswa kwemveliso wakho. 

6. Landa ukuthi ukhokhele ilungu lehlelo kwizinsizakalo zokuzixhasa. 

7. Emva kwalokho, qhagamshelana nesikhundla sokuzixhasa sokhokela ilungu lehlelo. Khumbula ukuba isikhundla sokuzixhasa kumele sikwazi ukukuph
